        <div1 type="body">
            

<p><placeName>Lexington</placeName> <date when="1826-01-26">26 January 1826</date></p>
<p><persName>Stephen F Austin Esqr</persName></p>

<p>Dear Sir Permit me to make you acquainted with my friend
<persName>William Haydon</persName> of <placeName>Jessamine County Kentucky</placeName> You will find him
an amiable Correct young gentleman he visits your <placeName>Grant</placeName> With an
intention of settling in the <placeName>Country</placeName> If pleased with it please render
him any services or attentions you may have in your power during
his stay with you and they will be thankfully Recollected If those
two <persName>gentlemen</persName> should returned pleased with the <placeName>Country</placeName> many persons will move to it from a <placeName>Rich part of this state</placeName> please speak of
me to your <persName>Brother</persName> the <persName>Barron</persName> and <persName>Don M Allouri</persName> and <persName>Mosquis</persName></p>

                           <p><persName>L. Hawkins</persName></p>


        </div1>
